@PORT=your_port_from_dotenv

@AUTH_USERNAME=user_from_htpasswd
@AUTH_PASSWORD=password

@EXTERNAL_DOMAIN=your_ip_or_domain
@TELEGRAM_SECRET=your_telegram_secret_from_dotenv

@CHAT_ID=from_telegram


### Local tests

### SMS forward
POST http://localhost:{{PORT}}/sms?number=%2B1234567890&chat_id={{CHAT_ID}}
Content-Type: text/plain

Text with line breaks
double quotes ", emooji ðŸ˜™ and a slash \

### Missed call forward (or any other text)
POST http://localhost:{{PORT}}/reply_from_macrodroid
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "chat_id": {{CHAT_ID}},
    "text": "Missed call from +1234567890"
}

### Telegram Webhook
POST http://localhost:{{PORT}}/telegram_webhook?secret={{TELEGRAM_SECRET}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "chat": {"id": {{CHAT_ID}}},
    "text": "/start"
  }
}


